{"tid":1251347,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Steam] 2D格鬥遊戲《百萬亞瑟王 Arcana Blood》上架，讓八神庵和大野晶並肩作戰","createTime":"2019-06-22T13:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T13:12:21.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f234bde92680ab687ebd9e4916741ae66f53983a","tid":1251347,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:12:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2364472640489910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2364472640489910&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3jQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=7a40fc97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2364472640489910</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtmMHEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtmMHEz.jpg&h=9b0de8f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSteam《百萬亞瑟王 Arcana Blood》上架，讓八神庵和大野晶並肩作戰<br />\n---<br />\n📣由 Square Enix 與 Team ARCANA 聯合製作的 2D 格鬥遊戲《百萬亞瑟王 Arcana Blood》自 2017 年 11 月接連推出街機版與 PS4 版後，PC 版已於今（20）日於 Steam 平台上架。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲以手遊《百萬亞瑟王》角色與世界觀作為主軸，還有與多款遊戲合作的異界角色，例如《聖劍傳說》莉絲、《拳皇 XIV》八神庵，還有動漫作品《高分少女》的大野晶等。可操控鬥士為 13 位，一次可從 31 名屬性不同的輔助角色選出三位。<br />\n<br />\n而除了劇情主線，遊戲還有訓練、線上對戰模式，以及大廳比賽，最多可支援 6 名玩家對戰。故事由《魔法禁書目錄》鎌池和馬監製，而著名作曲家下村陽子也有參與配樂部分。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲本體已於 Steam 平台上架，另售《百萬亞瑟王 Arcana Blood》限量版，加贈 2 張精美桌布與原聲帶精選集。有興趣的玩家可前往 Steam 商店參考。<br />\n<br />\nSteam:<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/989550/Million_Arthur_Arcana_Blood/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F989550%2FMillion_Arthur_Arcana_Blood%2F&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3jQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=c865b85b\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/989550/Million_Arthur_Arcana_Blood/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3xTnED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3xTnED.jpg&h=9e63998d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTqtVZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTqtVZE.jpg&h=48bfb7bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1i28bx0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1i28bx0.jpg&h=9b1e2593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UfGT66m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfGT66m.jpg&h=a7b41a3f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}